§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ A ❬convex cone❭ is a cone which is a convex set. ⦉

  ‖ A cone $A ⊂ 𝗥^d$ is pointed if $x, -x ∈ A ⟹ x = 0$.
